reviewText: Loved this show. Glad I found the DVDs. Wish Amazon would make other cancelled shows available.

I was very skeptical at first about watching a half-hour sitcom starring a major NFL icon such as Michael Strahan but I was definitely impressed by the comedic timing that he shares with the rest of the cast (including TV/film veteran Daryl "Chill" Mitchell). Like most recent new shows was cancelled abruptly. This was very disfortunate since the show was actually very funny.

I'm a big fan of Chill Mitchell, but an even bigger fan of CCH Pounder (since the 80's). Really cute show-- cleverly creative and funny-- great cast! Too bad it was only on for one season. Glad I purchased.
